Detailed Description

Data passed into a CUDA function callback function as the cbdata argument to Sanitizer_CallbackFunc. The cbdata will be this type for domain equal tp SANITIZER_CB_DOMAIN_RESOURCE and cbid equal to SANITIZER_CBID_RESOURCE_FUNCTIONS_LAZY_LOADED. The callback data is only valid within the invocation of the callback function that is passed the data. If you need to retain some data for use outside of the callback, you must make a copy of it.
